<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | SHOP.CO</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS styles for the 404 page */
        :root {
            /* Define colors based on the SHOP.CO aesthetic */
            --primary-text: #000;
            --secondary-text: #666;
            --background-color: #fff;
            --button-bg: #000;
            --button-text: #fff;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; /* A clean, universal font */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--primary-text);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 90%;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 50%;
        }

        /* Large, bold 404 number */
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.1em;
            letter-spacing: -3px; /* A touch of modern styling */
        }

        /* Main heading (H1) */
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Sub-text */
        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: var(--secondary-text);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Call-to-action button */
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1.3rem 30px;
            font-size: 1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--button-text);
            background-color: var(--button-bg);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #333; /* Slightly lighter on hover */
        }

        /* Logo/Branding - simple text based on the image */
        .logo {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-text);
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Mobile optimization */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .error-code {
                font-size: 6em;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <h1>Oops! Page Not Found.</h1>
        <p>The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable. Let's get you back to shopping!</p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Go Back To Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>